"order to use lead enrichment. To access the *CRM* settings, navigate to "
":menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Under the "
":guilabel:`CRM` section activate the :guilabel:`Leads` option and click "
":guilabel:`Save`."
