msgid ""
"By default, Odoo suggests you an automatic alert called *Take action on less"
" satisfied clients*."
msgstr ""
"De manera predeterminada, Odoo sugiere una alerta automática llamada "
"*Contactar a los clientes menos satisfechos*."

